Trace the parabola y = x² and use it for graphical solution of the following equations:
(1) x² - x - 2.25 = 0; (2) 2x² - 3x - 5 = 0;
(3) 3.1x² - 14x + 5.8 = 0; (4) 4x² - 12x + 9 = 0;
